ndon before he won any of his three major titles.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1850, \"end\": 1856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6278656846236554e-55, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9991976490774285, \"rank\": 0.00080023943290199, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He ended up winning the U.S. Open the following month, then won his famed 2013 Wimbledon title the next summer.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray was coming off his second Wimbledon title in 2016 when he won gold in Rio.\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6278656846236554e-55, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2125, \"end\": 2128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2680524140672919e-16, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Spaniard is also entering his last Olympics as he seemingly approaches retirement.\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Spaniard_(